                <h1 class="domdom">30</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1036">Mary &amp; Max</a></h1>

                <h2>30 Sep 2012, 6:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p><p><em>An absolute triumph: </em><span>A </span>hilarious and deeply affecting clay animated tale of friendship. Includes themes such as childhood neglect, loneliness, autism, depression
and anxiety.</p></p>

