                <h1 class="domdom">10</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/982">Steam Of Life + Discussion (2010)</a></h1>

                <h2>10 Oct 2012, 6:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>A Beautiful and poetic documentary which travels through Finland's saunas inviting (mostly naked) men from all walks of life to share their touching stories about birth, death, love and friendship.</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/982">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

