                <h1 class="domdom">17</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/984">Benny &amp; Joon (1993)</a></h1>

                <h2>17 Oct 2012, 6:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>A quirky romantic comedy about two people who, deemed as misfits by society, fall in love with each other. Johnny Depp stars in one of finest performances emulating the eccentric and slapstick humour of Charlie Chaplin and Buster Keaton.</p>

                <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/984">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

