                <h1 class="domdom">24</h1>

                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/985">Every Little Thing (1997)</a></h1>

                <h2>24 Oct 2012, 6:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p><p><span>An incredible intimate and profound documentary about one of the world’s most highly regarded psychiatric institutions. The film charts the events leading up to the annual summer play as both</span><span> patients and staff live and work together.</span></p></p>

