                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/986">Harvey</a></h1>

                <h2>28 Oct 2012, 6:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p>A timeless<span> black and white masterpiece. Starring
James Stewart in a career defining performance as Elwood P. Dowd,a mild-mannered, pleasant man, who just
happens to have an invisible friend resembling a six-foot rabbit. Hilariously uplifting, Harvey will do you the world of good.</span></p>

