                <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/1047">You, The Living (2007)</a></h1>

                <h2>7 Nov 2012, 6:30 p.m.</h2>

                <p><span>"Hilarious, Monty Python meets Ingmar Bergman… Utterly unique" UNCUT You, the Living is a film about humankind, its greatness, its baseness, it's joy, it's sorrow, its self-confidence, it's anxiety and its desire to love and be loved.</span></p>

